For the 1988 marketing year in the sheepmeat sector:
1.  the basic price is hereby fixed at 432,32 ECU per 100 kilograms carcase weight;
2.  the intervention price is hereby fixed at 367,47 ECU per 100 kilograms carcase weight;
3.  the derived intervention price applicable in region 4 is hereby fixed at 347,66 ECU per 100 kilograms carcase weight.
